he potential economic value of their research findings. The Industry Liaison Office also promotes ongoing collaboration between business and academia. Industry Liaison Office Industry on Campus In connection with the Industry on Campus professorships, we are creating new collaborative projects wtih industry at the interface of basic and application-oriented research. This provides excellent opportunities for the University of Tübingen to find new ways for industrial partnerships to go and to open up new perspectives for applications-inspired research. Industry on Campus Technology Transfer The Technology Transfer office provides information, advice and support to industry partners, inventors, researchers, and start-up entrepreneurs when it comes to cooperation between business and academia. Technology Transfer Contact Business Contacts Praxis Portal Industry on Campus Industry Liaison Office Technology Transfer Key services Official bulletins Disabled access Advice for international students Media Semester Dates Jobs Organizing Your Studies University Library Programs available Welcome Center for Scholars Further services System status Corporate Design Conference materials Maps Cafeteria menu Newsletter Uni Tübingen aktuell Studium Generale Uni shop Calendar of events Portals ALMA Exchange Mail (OWA) Research information system FIT ILIAS, moodle Search for persons at the University (EPV) Praxisportal Timms Video Portal Webmail Uni Tübingen Contact us University of Tübingen Geschwister-Scholl-Platz 72074 Tübingen Germany Phone: +49 7071 29-0 Contact us Facebook Twitter Youtube Instagram LinkedIn Mastodon © 2024 Eberhard Karls Universität Tübingen, Tübingen Imprint Data Privacy Statement Barrierefreiheit RSS-Feed Shortcut Print	{podcasts,fördermöglichkeiten,professors,datenschutzbeauftragter,teilnahmevoraussetzungen,forschungsschwerpunkte,webmail,hochschulweiterbildung,entrepreneurs,professorships,doctorates,humanities,biology,academics,semesters,germany,teacher,libra